OL,7,FVehicles are forced to swerve round a
OL,8,Fcar, which was stopped in the middle
OL,9,Fof the M4. Video from Wiltshire Police
OL,11,FCCTV shows the moment a woman, who had
OL,12,Ftaken ten times the legal amount of
OL,13,FKetamine, stopped her car in the
OL,14,Fmiddle of a busy motorway.
OL,16,FCars and lorries can be seen swerving
OL,17,Fjust metres from the car after Bethan
OL,18,FMarkfort, of Reigate, Surrey, stopped
OL,19,Fher car in lane two of the M4, in the
OL,20,Fvideo captured on April 18.
