OL,7,FWitnesses had called the police and
OL,8,Fwhen officers arrived between Membury
OL,9,Fand junction 15 for Swindon, they
OL,10,Fsuspected Markfort was under the
OL,11,Finfluence.
OL,13,FTests revealed Markfort, who had
OL,14,Ftravelled from Surrey, had more than
OL,15,Ften times the legal limit of ketamine
OL,16,Ffor driving in her blood at the time
OL,17,Fof the incident.
