OL,7,FShe was then charged and appeared at
OL,8,FSwindon Magistrates' Court on October
OL,9,F7, where she pleaded guilty to drug
OL,10,Fdriving.
OL,12,FShe was disqualified from driving for
OL,13,Ftwo years, fined #1,200, required to
OL,14,Fpay a surcharge of #480 and court
OL,15,Fcosts of #85.
OL,17,FRoads Policing Officer Tom Webster
OL,18,Fsaid: "Markfort's actions were
OL,19,Fincredibly reckless and dangerous and
OL,20,Fput a number of lives, including her
OL,21,Fown, at risk.
