OL,7,F"It is extremely fortunate that having
OL,8,Fstopped in the second lane for unknown
OL,9,Freasons, the drivers behind her were
OL,10,Fable to react in time to take evasive
OL,11,Faction, potentially averting a serious
OL,12,Fcollision.
OL,14,F"There can be no excuse for driving
OL,15,Funder the influence of drugs, let
OL,16,Falone the distance Markfort travelled
OL,17,Fwith the amount of ketamine she had in
OL,18,Fher system."
